---
title: Quick Chipotle Chicken Breast Soup with Homemade Tortilla Chips and Kidney Beans
description: On the table in less than 25 minutes, this Quick Chipotle Chicken Breast Soup is quick but still full of flavour. Chipotle is full of rich, smoky and fruity flavours with a kick from the chipotle chillies.
